column1: #Remove this guide before uploading this file.
#username: Username of the User which should be unique.
#email: A valid email address of the User.
#phone_number: Phone number of user(without country code).
#country_coder: Country code of respective phone number
#role_id:role_id should be a valid number and must be associated with created role.
#password: Password must have Min length:8 Special Char: 1 Lower Case: 1 Upper Case:1 Number:1.Allowed characters are a-z
#force_password_reset_on_next_login: should be a string between True or False.
